-antwhen.content:
**When is Ant going to play/record/post a video/whatever?**

- We don't know. Neither Staff or other members of the server have the answer. Ant will do what he wants to do when he's ready to do it. If you want Ant's content, please respect that and let him do his work without pressuring him!
- You can keep an eye on <#871141617170513950> for game announcements and check his Youtube page for new videos in the meantime.

-howstaff.content:
**How can I become a staff member/moderator?**

- There are no staff applications.
- When the staff team decides more staff members are needed, they will ask a few active users who have demonstrated trustworthiness, maturity, good decision making, and good behavior.
- If you consistently demonstrate those qualities, the staff team might ask you to become a helper!

-howranks.content:
**How do I get ranks in Ant's Discord?**

- To get ranks, all you need to do is chat! The more you chat, the more XP you get. And once you have a certain amount of XP, you get a rank!
- You can check your rank progress in <#956020494254104586> by using the command `t!rank` and the Tatsu bot will tell you.
You can also do the command `t!leveledroles` to see what ranks exist, or you can do the command `t!top` to see the rank leaderboard.

-joinbw.content:
**Want to play Bedwars with Ant? Here's how:**

- When Ant is hosting a match, he'll post a game code in <#871141617170513950>. Copy this code and log in to Bedwars. Click the Green Play button below then click "Custom Match". A window will pop up which is where you can enter the game code to join Ant.
- Make sure you join fast- once the game starts, Ant will lock the server so the game can start. He will NOT unlock the server for you if you missed it!

-joinmm2.content:
**How do I play MM2 with Ant?**

- When Ant is hosting a game of MM2, he'll post a join link in <#871141617170513950>. Click that link to join the game.
- Try to be fast! The game fills up quickly!
